Class UniversityStudent

java.lang.Object
Student
UniversityStudent
public class UniversityStudent extends Student
Concrete implementation of the Student class representing a University Student. Includes specific logic for calculating connection strengths based on university criteria.

  • Method Details

    • calculateConnectionStrength

      public int calculateConnectionStrength(Student other)
      Calculates the connection strength between this student and another based on:
      • Roommate: +4
      • Shared Internship: +3 per internship
      • Same Major: +2
      • Same Age: +1
      Specified by:
      calculateConnectionStrength in class Student
      Parameters:
      other - The student to compare against.
      Returns:
      The total connection strength score.
